{"tid":1216951,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 連登沉默大多數向專業的無綫新聞仝人致敬","createTime":"2019-06-13T11:29:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T06:16:25.000Z","uid":550,"like":15,"dislike":130,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"6950f548616f5ce3fae3533332dbc89dc2401196","tid":1216951,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:29:31.000Z","msg":"鑑於近日大批暴徒於連登散播暴力言論，並加以攻擊無綫新聞的一眾新聞從業者，我謹代表連登沉默大多數反擊相關悖論，無綫新聞素有「事事關心」的美譽，一直為國家和香港的忠心朋友，優化港人的愛國情懷，提高廣大同胞的國民素質，媲美我國的央視新聞。無綫電視記者縱被污衊，今日《六點半新聞報道》仍有報道引述連登言論，故特此撰文鼓勵貴台記者士氣。希望一眾連登會員及廣大市民看到無綫記者可致以慰問和支持，現附上無綫記者圖片數張，予以參考。<br />\n管理層<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/189364/org/48d569868eafe7302a8cd42cecf927a0.JPG/pS1itXjGdU-UwAme-vsU48DSP6ZOYZyP0RuNmdEbjZk?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F189364%2Forg%2F48d569868eafe7302a8cd42cecf927a0.JPG%2FpS1itXjGdU-UwAme-vsU48DSP6ZOYZyP0RuNmdEbjZk%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=a970e0f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">袁志偉</span> （助理總經理(新聞及資訊)） <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/news_res/2018/07/04/301254/i_567x377_082933691.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Fnews_res%2F2018%2F07%2F04%2F301254%2Fi_567x377_082933691.jpg&h=7fc82476&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黃淑明</span> （總監） <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/24vgBHQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F24vgBHQ.png&h=714a9913&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">許方輝</span>（助理總監）"},{"pid":"aeb98a24bfa4939a7dcf1b34a437e64f035cf43d","tid":1216951,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":36,"score":-36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T11:41:56.000Z","msg":"主播<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CEONJru.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCEONJru.png&h=c0edb5f2&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: 